    "doc": "ACIM V/HZ Control",
    "title": "Description",
    "content": "AC Induction Motor (ACIM) is controlled using VHz control. Motor start/stop operation is controlled by the switch and motor speed can be changed by the on-board potentiometer. Waveforms and variables can be monitored runtime using X2CScope. Key features enabled in this project are: . | VHz Control | . ",
